import React, { useEffect, useState } from 'react'; import { useParams, useNavigate } from 'react-router-dom'; const FinanceDealDetails = () => { const { dealId } = useParams(); const navigate = useNavigate(); const [deal, setDeal] = useState(null); const [loading, setLoading] = useState(true); const [error, setError] = useState(null); useEffect(() => { setLoading(true); fetch(`/api/deals/${dealId}`) .then(res => { if (!res.ok) throw new Error('Deal not found'); return res.json(); }) .then(data => setDeal(data.deal || data.data || data)) .catch(err => setError(err.message)) .finally(() => setLoading(false)); }, [dealId]); if (loading) return
Loading...
; if (error) return
Error: {error}
; if (!deal) return
Deal not found.
; return (

Deal Details

{deal.vehicle || `${deal.year} ${deal.make} ${deal.model}`}

Stock Number

{deal.rpStockNumber || deal.stockNumber || 'N/A'}

VIN

{deal.vin || 'N/A'}

Purchase Price

${deal.purchasePrice?.toLocaleString() || 'N/A'}

List Price

${deal.listPrice?.toLocaleString() || 'N/A'}

Kill Price

${deal.killPrice?.toLocaleString() || 'N/A'}

Deal Type

{deal.dealType || 'N/A'}

Stage

{deal.currentStage || 'N/A'}

Salesperson

{deal.salesperson || 'N/A'}

Seller Info

Name

{deal.seller?.name || 'N/A'}

Type

{deal.seller?.type || 'N/A'}

Contact

{deal.seller?.contact?.address || 'N/A'}

{deal.seller?.contact?.phone || 'N/A'}

{deal.seller?.contact?.email || 'N/A'}

Dates

Purchase Date

{deal.purchaseDate ? new Date(deal.purchaseDate).toLocaleDateString() : 'N/A'}

Created

{deal.createdAt ? new Date(deal.createdAt).toLocaleDateString() : 'N/A'}

Notes

{deal.generalNotes || 'None'}

Workflow History

{deal.workflowHistory && deal.workflowHistory.length > 0 ? (
    {deal.workflowHistory.map((entry, idx) => (
  • {entry.stage} — {entry.timestamp ? new Date(entry.timestamp).toLocaleString() : 'N/A'}
    By: {entry.changedBy || 'N/A'}
    {entry.notes || ''}
    • ))}
) : (

No workflow history.

)}
); }; export default FinanceDealDetails;
